reviewText: A must for all Man U fans.
Got this as a gift for my grandson.. He was so excited he  started watching the DVD's the day it arrived..
meaning, I AM the greatest Godmother EVER!... at least that was the reaction I received when he opened his present.

Great DVD set to learn about all the great players at united.
The only thing that disappointed me about the box set was that the cover was made only from a cardboard like material. It barely supports itself without the DVD's placed inside of them.
